                    <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='11'>Customers are at high risk</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='12'>Finding:</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#75a1c7' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='11'>Using Python and Machine Learning, the model has identified 1200 customers at high risk to churn with ROC.AUC score of 0.8.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='12'>Recommendation:</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#75a1c7' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='11'>Model identifies ~1,200 high-risk customers before they churn — enabling pre-emptive retentions methods to retain them.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='12'>Expected Impact:</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#75a1c7' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='11'>Increase in the retention of the customers which were prediccted to churn.</run>
                  </formatted-text>
